      "Read encoding at offset 12 (BE uint32): 1 = μ-law, 27 = A-law",
      "Read sample rate at offset 16: 8000 Hz for G.711 telephony",
      "Data starts at dataOffset (typically 24): raw 8-bit μ-law samples"
    ]
